p_{X|Y}(x|y) = P(X=x|Y=y) = \frac{P(X=x,Y=y)}{P(Y=y)} = \frac{p(x,y)}{\sum_x p(x,y)}
p_X(x) = \sum_y p(x,y)
p(y|X) = \frac{p(x,y)}{\sum_y p(x,y)}
